Whenever you play an attack action card with base power 6 or more {p}, roll a 6 sided die. On;
1 to 4 - Halve the attack's base {p}, rounded down.
5 or 6 - Double the attack's base {p}.

Choose 1;
* Target club or hammer weapon attack gains +3{p}.
* Target attack action card with cost 2 or greater gains +3{p} and "When this hits a hero, they discard a card."

Choose 1;
* Target club or hammer weapon attack gains +2{p}.
* Target attack action card with cost 2 or greater gains +2{p} and "When this hits a hero, they discard a card."

Choose 1;
* Target sword or dagger weapon attack gains +2{p}.
* Target attack action card with cost {r} or less gains +2{p} and "If this hits, this attack gains **go again**."
